{"tid":1103088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議員倡全港學生派2500元 楊潤雄：可再考慮","createTime":"2019-04-12T07:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T11:23:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8c37bd7e289ba72f9d9396df21cce1183d385932","tid":1103088,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】立法會財委會特別會議早上討論財政預算案中的教育內容。教育局局長楊潤雄在會上被問及，給基層學生派發2500元的措施，能否擴大至全港學生時解釋，財政司長以紓困原則提出相關措施，所以只針對有經濟需要的學生；將來會否擴闊派錢範圍，可再考慮。<br />\n對於校本管理制度下，不時傳出學校行政管理混亂問題，楊潤雄強調，教育局一直無減輕監管學校的工作，但認為毋須每次都大鑼大鼓地去做。<br />\n楊潤雄以近日一所備受傳媒關注的小學為例，指當局早於傳媒報道前已作調查。他認為，若純粹因為傳媒報道的個案而指責政府監管失效並不公平。他又指，局方重視與教師溝通，正考慮再增加雙方的溝通機會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vGUsl6qvuWBRLdolxKM5Og--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190412a103655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvGUsl6qvuWBRLdolxKM5Og--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190412a103655.jpg&h=c321b5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊潤雄強調，教育局對學校的監管工作一直無減輕。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%80%A1%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BE2500%E5%85%83-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E5%8F%AF%E5%86%8D%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE-023700578.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BE2500%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584-%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE-023700578.html&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8EKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=cedbc624\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%80%A1%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BE2500%E5%85%83-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84-%E5%8F%AF%E5%86%8D%E8%80%83%E6%8